---
name: Newsletter subscribtion form
description: |
  The standard newsletter subscription form.

  This example only provides the essentials of the form component. Making this subscription form fully functional requires some additional functionality. See the [Basket example](https://github.com/mozilla/basket-example/) for more.
notes: |
  - Some newsletters are only available in one language, so don’t require a language selection.
links:
    Newsletter Demo: /demos/newsletter.html
---

<aside class="mzp-c-newsletter">
  <div class="mzp-c-newsletter-image">
    <img src="{{@root.baseurl}}/static/img/newsletter/newsletter-image.png" width="346" height="346" alt="">
  </div>

  <form id="newsletter-form" class="mzp-c-newsletter-form mzp-c-form" name="newsletter-form" action="/path/to/handler/" method="post">
    <header class="mzp-c-newsletter-header">
      <h3 class="mzp-c-newsletter-title">Love the Web?</h3>
      <p class="mzp-c-newsletter-tagline">Get the Mozilla newsletter and help us keep it open and free.</p>
    </header>

    <fieldset class="mzp-c-newsletter-content">
      <div class="mzp-c-form-errors" id="newsletter-errors">{{#if errors}}{{#block "errors"}}{{/block}}{{/if}}</div>

      {{#embed "patterns.molecules.forms.fields.input" id="email" type="email" required="true" addclass="mzp-js-email-field"}}
        {{#content "label"}}Your email address{{/content}}
        {{#content "attrs"}}placeholder="yourname@example.com"{{/content}}
      {{/embed}}

      <div id="newsletter-details" class="mzp-c-newsletter-details">
        {{#embed "patterns.molecules.forms.fields.select" id="country" name="country" required="true"}}
          {{#content "label"}}Country{{/content}}
          {{#content "options"}}
            {{#each (data "items")}}
              <option value="{{country}}">{{country}}</option>
            {{/each}}
              <option>And so on...</option>
          {{/content}}
        {{/embed}}
        {{#embed "patterns.molecules.forms.fields.select" id="language" name="lang" required="true"}}
          {{#content "label"}}Language{{/content}}
          {{#content "options"}}
            {{#each (data "items")}}
              <option value="{{language}}">{{language}}</option>
            {{/each}}
          {{/content}}
        {{/embed}}
        <fieldset class="mzp-c-choices mzp-l-choices-inline">
          <legend class="mzp-c-form-label">Format</legend>
          {{#embed "patterns.molecules.forms.fields.choice" id="format-html" name="fmt" type="radio" value="H"}}{{#content "label"}}HTML{{/content}}{{/embed}}
          {{#embed "patterns.molecules.forms.fields.choice" id="format-text" name="fmt" type="radio" value="T"}}{{#content "label"}}Text{{/content}}{{/embed}}
        </fieldset>
        {{#embed "patterns.molecules.forms.fields.choice" id="privacy" name="privacy" type="checkbox" required="true" is-legal="true"}}{{#content "label"}}I’m okay with Mozilla handling my info as explained in <a href="https://www.mozilla.org/privacy/websites/">this Privacy Notice</a>{{/content}}{{/embed}}
      </div>

      <p class="mzp-c-form-submit">
        <button type="submit" class="mzp-c-button" id="newsletter-submit">Sign up now</button>
        <span class="mzp-c-fieldnote">We will only send you Mozilla-related information.</span>
      </p>
    </fieldset>
  </form>

  <div id="newsletter-thanks" class="mzp-c-newsletter-thanks">
    <h3>Thanks!</h3>
    <p>If you haven’t previously confirmed a subscription to a Mozilla-related newsletter you may have to do so. Please check your inbox or your spam filter for an email from us.</p>
  </div>

</aside>

<script src="{{@root.baseurl}}/assets/protocol/protocol/js/protocol-newsletter.js"></script>
